# /facts Command

When the user types `/facts` followed by any text, append that text as a new fact to `context/FACTS.md`.

## Format

Add each fact as a bullet point with a timestamp:

```
- [YYYY-MM-DD] <fact text>
```

## Example

User: `/facts Tau prefers functional programming patterns`

Append to FACTS.md:
```
- [2026-02-02] Tau prefers functional programming patterns
```

## Instructions

1. Extract the text after `/facts `
2. Append it to `context/FACTS.md` as a new bullet point with today's date
3. Confirm to the user that the fact was added
